  "body": "<div id=\"post-view220998338535\" class=\"post-view pcol2 _param(1) _postViewArea220998338535\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div style=\"font-size:10pt; font-family:'957317_10';\" class=\"view\"><p style=\"text-align: center; \" align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">안녕하세요 이수한의원입니다</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center; \" align=\"center\"><br /></p><p style=\"text-align: center; \" align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">이번달 3일 ( 석가탄신일 ) 과 5일 ( 어린이 날 ) 에는 공휴일이라&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center; \" align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">저희 이수한의원도 쉽니다</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center; \" align=\"center\"><br /></p><p style=\"text-align: center; \" align=\"center\"><br /></p><p style=\"text-align: center; \" align=\"center\"><br /></p><p style=\"text-align: center; \" align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">9일 ( 대통령 선거날 ) 은 오후 4시까지 진료하니&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center; \" align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">아래 있는 진료 시간표을 참고해주세요</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center; \" align=\"center\"><br /></p><p style=\"text-align: center; \" align=\"center\"><br /></p><p style=\"text-align: center; \" align=\"center\"><br /></p><p style=\"text-align: center; \" align=\"center\"><br /></p><p style=\"text-align: center; \" align=\"center\"><br /></p><p style=\"text-align: center; \" align=\"center\"><br /></p><p style=\"text-align: center; \" align=\"center\"><img src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/MjAxNzA1MDRfMjYw/MDAxNDkzODc3NDI3NzEy.eAcpGWUjLEZ38M_ly55hcbLhk6p8Kl52yuB5AndMBC0g.LsggrX2rt5Y8fOXvl8PFRcmi79lvo8D-iv5XkVeY4yog.JPEG.isuhani/CCI20170504.jpg?type=w80_blur\" width=\"550\" height=\"386\" align=\"center\" style=\"cursor: pointer; border-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); rwidth:550px; rheight:386px;\" id=\"MjAxNzA1MDRfMjYw/MDAxNDkzODc3NDI3NzEy.eAcpGWUjLEZ38M_ly55hcbLhk6p8Kl52yuB5AndMBC0g.LsggrX2rt5Y8fOXvl8PFRcmi79lvo8D-iv5XkVeY4yog.JPEG.isuhani/CCI20170504.jpg\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_